<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Inventory Management</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            height:100vh;
            display: flex;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .left-content {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top:-10%;
        }

            .left-content h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
                color: #333;
            }

            .left-content p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                color: #555;
                margin: 20px 0;
            }

        .btn {
            width:30%;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

            .btn:hover {
                background: #0056b3;
                color:white;
            }

        .right-image {
            flex: 1;
            height:80vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background: #f0f0f0;
        }

            .right-image img {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 500px;
            }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="left-content">
            <h1>Manage Your Inventory Effortlessly</h1>
            <p>Track products, manage vendors & customers, and streamline your inventory workflow with our powerful system.</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn">Get Started</a>
        </div>

        <div class="right-image">
            <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRBoClvWwMTqrXphMMAsNjC4GLftopIzdqj3w&s" alt="Inventory Management">
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
